page.title: 11A Day in my life in 1985.
page.content: At{7.45 am.}my mum comes in my bedroom and wakes me up for school. I don't get up straight away - I lie in bed reading my favourite book. At{8.00 am} I get up and go into the bathroom. I brush my teeth and wash my face. In 5 minutes I'm dressed and go downstairs for my breakfast, with my brother Adrian. At{8.20}Dawn comes to call for me and we set off for school. When I got home from school my mum had fishcakes and chips ready for my tea. They were very nice. Dawn came round at{4.50}and we played golf till{6.30.} Then we went to Dawn's house and her Dad asked me if I wanted to go roller skating at Adwick with them. But my mum said I couldn't as I would be going to Sheffield on Saturday and I had to go dancing. My mum took me, and my dad picked me up at{8.45pm.}Then I watched T.V. I went to bed at{9.30pm.
